OL,5, Parents in England whose children miss 
OL,6, school face harsher penalties depending
OL,7, on where they live, a BBC Panorama     
OL,8, investigation has found.               
OL,10,FFines, which begin at #60, but rise if 
OL,11,Fnot paid promptly, totalled more than  
OL,12,F#8.6m in the past school year.         
OL,14,FBut some local councils told us no     
OL,15,Fpenalties had been issued, while other 
OL,16,Fauthorities handed out thousands.      
OL,18,FEven when differences in population are
OL,19,Ftaken into account, there remain       
OL,20,Fdisparities in the number of fines.    
